OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FMore than 100 people have become ill,
OL,7,Fwith some being admitted to hospital,
OL,8,Fafter an outbreak of E.coli thought to
OL,9,Fbe linked to a nationally distributed
OL,10,Ffood, the UK Health Security Agency
OL,11,F(UKHSA) has said.
OL,13,FThe majority of the 113 cases detected
OL,14,Fsince May 25 have been linked to a
OL,15,F"single outbreak".
OL,17,FCase numbers are expected to continue
OL,18,Frising.
