OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FAll the cases recorded in the outbreak
OL,7,Finvolve Shiga toxin-producing E. coli
OL,8,FO145 (Stec), with 81 cases in England,
OL,9,F18 in Wales, 13 in Scotland and one
OL,10,Fperson in Northern Ireland who
OL,11,Fbelieves they acquired Stec in England.
OL,13,FAre cases expected to rise? ITV News
OL,14,FReporter Ellie Pitt explains
OL,16,FWhat is E.Coli?
OL,18,FE.coli is a diverse group of bacteria
OL,19,Fthat are usually harmless and live in
OL,20,Fthe intestines of humans and animals.
