OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FSome strains however, produce toxins
OL,7,Fthat can make people very ill, such as
OL,8,FStec.
OL,10,FIf people have been infected with
OL,11,FE.coli they will usually be aware
OL,12,Fwithin three to four days, but
OL,13,Fsymptoms can appear as late as two
OL,14,Fweeks after.
