OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FComing into contact with infected
OL,7,Fpeople, drinking water from
OL,8,Finadequately treated water supplies,
OL,9,Fand swimming in contaminated water can
OL,10,Falso spread E.coli.
OL,12,FThe UKHSA, however, has said there was
OL,13,Fcurrently no evidence linking the
OL,14,Foutbreak to open farms, drinking water
OL,15,For swimming in contaminated sea, lakes
OL,16,For rivers.
OL,18,FHow dangerous is E.Coli?
