OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,FA small proportion of adults may
OL,7,Fdevelop a similar condition called
OL,8,Fthrombotic thrombocytopaenic purpura
OL,9,F(TTP).
OL,11,FSome people can become infected but
OL,12,Fdon't develop any symptoms.
OL,14,FWhat are medical professionals and the
OL,15,Fgovernment saying?
OL,17,FTrish Mannes, incident director at
OL,18,FUKHSA, said: "If you have diarrhoea
OL,19,Fand vomiting, you can take steps to
OL,20,Favoid passing it on to family and
OL,21,Ffriends.
