OL,3,CUK-wide E.coli outbreak: What do we
OL,4,Cknow so far?
OL,6,F"NHS.uk has information on what to do
OL,7,Fif you have symptoms and when to seek
OL,8,Fmedical advice.
OL,10,F"Do not return to work, school or
OL,11,Fnursery until 48 hours after your
OL,12,Fsymptoms have stopped."
OL,14,FJim McMenamin, Head of Health
OL,15,FProtection (infection Services),
OL,16,FPublic Health Scotland, said: "To help
OL,17,Fstop infections like E. coli from
OL,18,Fspreading, we advise regular hand
OL,19,Fwashing using soap and water,
OL,20,Fparticularly after using the toilet
OL,21,Fand before preparing food.
